parameters: $gameVariables.setValue(21, "KaShOp.Woah! It’s as big as the other room.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeWoEx.Kaley... I found an old staff here too. It may have belonged to this guy.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KaWoOp.You found a staff? Like a magic staff?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeWoEx.I gave it to another treasure hunter.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeBaEx.The girl we saw trespassing on the island from before.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KaAnEx.Of course I can. We’re already keeping secrets!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeFrEx.Clare and I are looking for the treasure of Nadia.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeFlEx.It’s a massive treasure worth a bazillion dollars.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeFrEx.Okay... I don’t know how much it’s worth. But Sofia is involved and she wouldn't be involved in anything that isn't big.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KaAnDe.Dammit 1Hero. You’re so bad at keeping secrets.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KaAnDe.You’re going to tell Mom about me and my problem.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeWoEx.No! Kaley. I’ve not said a word. I promise.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KaAnEx.Okay 1Hero. I won't tell anyone about the Chronicles of Narnia as long as you don’t embarrass me about my own problems.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeAnDe.It’s called the treasure of Nadia and it’s a real thing.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KaBaEx.We better get out of here. Alia is probably telling her Mom all about the dead guy.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeWoCl.Kaley. I did tell one other person about... your issue.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeFrEx.Yeah. Doctor Amor. She wants to help you.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeFrEx.She’s a sex doctor. She knows everything about sex.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeFlEx.Oh yeah. I know from first hand experience. She knows her stuff.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeFrEx.Of course. You can trust her. I trust her.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeFrOp.I think it’s important Kaley. Will you do it for me?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeFrEx.I care about you 1Kaley. I want you to be happy. ");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeFrOp.The happy girl I knew when we were kids is still there. I know it.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KaAnDe.1Hero! Don’t be mushy. You’ll make me throw up.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeFrOp.Come on dumbface. Let’s get out of here.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeBaDe<.I don’t know if this is a pirate, Cape Vedra native, or Tikpak tribesman. But it has to be one of those.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeWoOp.There is a whirling vortex of water. I can’t cross here.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeWoEx.Go on! Jump in the water and swim to the other side.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KaWoCl.But you said the water is freezing!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeWoEx.Not here. It’s only that one pool.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeWoEx.It’s not that deep. Just go for it!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeFrEx.You can do it Alia. I won't let you drown.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeBaEx.Come on! The exit is this way.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "CrBaOp.This is the remains of a Tikpak warship.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "CrBaEx.I believe their final battle was here.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeFrEx.If some of the Tikpak tribe survived, they may have moved the treasure.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "CrBaEx.The pirate ship is somewhere in this cave. It’s just a matter of finding the right clues to lead us there.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeBaOp.What do you know about the Tikpak language?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeWoCl.Well... Uhh... If they put a curse on the treasure then it must have some magical properties.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "CrAnDe.Yes. One might believe the language to be supernatural.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeBaOp.What type of magic are we talking about?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "CrAnOp.Why the sudden interest in the Tikpak 1Hero?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeHaEx.Seems like something worth investigating... Doesn’t it?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "CrBaEx.I spent most of my life investigating it. And it’s led me here.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "CrAnDe.And now I’m on the verge of finding the biggest treasure the world has ever known.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeBaEx.That treasure can cause some serious damage if the curse is real.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "CrAnEx.The curse needs to be unloaded onto some unsuspecting low lifes.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeFlOp.I know. And that’s why I have the perfect plan.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeFlEx.We’re going to give it to the Eclipse Guild.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "CrAnOp.Fuck that! I’m not doing business with them.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeAnEx.They killed my father! This is the perfect revenge.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "CrMaOp.God damn it! You’re not going to fuck up my discovery for your own personal revenge!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "CrAnOp.It’s the perfect plan to get us killed!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeBaEx.My life is already on the line. Are you prepared to risk your life to maximize your payoff?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeFrEx.The Eclipse Guild has the money. You’re not going to get as much through any other buyers.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "CrAnOp.I can get enough without risking involving the Guild.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeAnOp.That curse is going to kill people Clare. Who are you willing to sacrifice to make a little bit of cash?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "CrAnOp.Don’t get self righteous with me. You’re going to kill the entire Eclipse Guild?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "CrAnOp.You don’t think innocent people will get caught up in it?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "CrAnDe.I don’t trust you 1Hero. I don’t trust your motives.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "CrAnEx.They are murderers 1Hero. If they die an early death... I can live with myself.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeFrEx.Diana knows the Guild. She will help us.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeSaOp.It’s not just about the money... Both of our lives depend on it.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "CrBaDe.I’m not in this for your lives. I’m in it for the treasure.");
